" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637cec8b00f026e4ddb4ea67b7d44bce3c0cdea6","tid":1263603,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"336870c5aa2bbe55d09ba07464cf5bffc19cdb0f","tid":1263603,"uid":13038,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"樓主開第三個post屌梁頌恆<br />\n話唔係私怨或者分化都冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:33:18.000Z","msg":"可能情傷呢"},{"pid":"a6741874d57ad1b1238017950c7890124ebfd831","tid":1263603,"uid":13038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"336870c5aa2bbe55d09ba07464cf5bffc19cdb0f","tid":1263603,"uid":13038,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"樓主開第三個post屌梁頌恆<br />\n話唔係私怨或者分化都冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:33:32.000Z","msg":"sor我錯 原來已經有四個post了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4f4c408048a7e637e56e777a9087286efb18a7","tid":1263603,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"關於「六二六」後續<br />\n<br />\n我們認為抗爭者應遵循不被捕原則行動。不過，昨晚警方態度惡劣，又在無預警情況下使用胡椒噴霧攻擊市民，收到有關消息的楊逸朗（Joe Yeung）心切保護同伴，他本意殿後，並呼籲在場人士率先撤退：「幾多人來就幾多人走！」<br />\n<br />\n可惜並非每位義士都像議員一樣，能夠借法律所賦予的權力以一擋百，何況昨晚連鄺議員也遭警員無視其合法要求、並且遭警員用粗口辱罵；後來在場義士決意留守，蒙受警察抄寫個人資料、甚至秋後算帳的後果。不過無論如何，我們應尊重這些義士的決定，畢竟他們每一位都心繫香港，才會親身出現在現場。<br />\n<br />\n不恥笑，不辱罵，尊重義士決定，採取合理方法保護義士。<br />\n<br />\n我們必須謹記，這場運動我們不僅追求撤回反送中條例，更追求「釋放所有義士及政治犯」、「成立獨立調查委員會、追究警方濫權濫捕」以及修訂「公安條例」。民眾抗爭、集會的權益，我們理應一同爭取，反對政治檢控；且維持聯繫團結一志，力抗內鬨排除抹黑。<br />\n<br />\n本陣線的成立由始至終為的是第一條原則：「我們永遠站在抗爭者的一方。」<br />\n<br />\n_<br />\n<br />\n澄清：本機制並非大台，目標在於引領多方合作，是次活動由群眾自發，政治人物負責協助召集，至現場梁已無用咪對群眾說話。現場沒有大台。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭聯合陣線"},{"pid":"d49df49c031a0fbcb42e711578b7ee8ed6da2a80","tid":1263603,"uid":51380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"336870c5aa2bbe55d09ba07464cf5bffc19cdb0f","tid":1263603,"uid":13038,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"樓主開第三個post屌梁頌恆<br />\n話唔係私怨或者分化都冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"點止兩個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689ff1f38ab35a7efecf384526e785b8eaf2a04a","tid":1263603,"uid":51380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d49df49c031a0fbcb42e711578b7ee8ed6da2a80","tid":1263603,"uid":51380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"336870c5aa2bbe55d09ba07464cf5bffc19cdb0f","tid":1263603,"uid":13038,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"樓主開第三個post屌梁頌恆<br />\n話唔係私怨或者分化都冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"點止兩個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:04:16.000Z","msg":"點止<span style=\"color: red;\">三</span>個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌 自柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3904cea76f01f385eb19b187f014bb880cfee3b7","tid":1263603,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi